<h3>Open tweets in your favourite Twitter app</h3>

<p>You can use Prowl Redirections to open your Tweets in an iPhone Twitter client instead of Prowl.</p>

<p>Use the app name "Prey Fetcher" to redirect all notifications from Prey Fetcher to <a href="http://forums.cocoaforge.com/viewtopic.php?f=45&amp;t=20704">any app Prowl supports</a>. You can also use "Prey Fetcher DM" specifically for DM notifications or "Prey Fetcher mention" for mentions â€” in case, for example, you only want DMs to open your Twitter app.</p>

